  "description": "The prism fish in its natural habitat — sunlit shallows, refracted light dancing on a sandy bottom. Moderate saw fold, medium-speed LFO1 at 0.35 Hz creating continuous spectral shimmer. Gentle bounce clicks like light catching on wave faces. Phaser warm and rolling. This is the 'face' of XOblique.",
